  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bae \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u00a0 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b86\u0baf\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Study to select village officer units and distribute fuel in Yalhi",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna. The District Secretary K. Mahesan has explored the possibility of allocating Village Officer units to the fuel filling stations in the district and distributing fuel through them with S. Sivatharan, Northern Regional Manager of Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation.",
        "From 01st Monday, fuel distribution will be done all over the country only on the basis of vehicle final digits and not on the basis of 'QR' method.",
        "Jaffna to ensure fuel availability to all and avoid wastage of time. The District Secretary is actively investigating.",
        "Based on that, it is hoped that both of these can be made possible by organizing the fuel distribution by the village officer divisionally.",
        "Village officer units surrounding each filling station will be allotted time. During that time, residents can get fuel for their vehicles at the designated fuel station. A fuel card can be used as an identity card to confirm their residency.",
        "Only one day in a week is allotted to a village officer division. Fuel will be distributed as per national 'QR' practice.",
        "Meanwhile, it has also been decided not to disclose the details of when the fuel bowser will arrive at the filling station.",
        "It has also been considered that it would be appropriate to carry out fuel supply from morning to evening at the specified fuel station on the day after the arrival of the fuel bowser under the supervision of the Divisional Secretariat.",
        "Also, in relation to maintenance of separate queues for men and women and maintenance of separate queues for essential services at petrol filling stations, it has been investigated."
      ],
